sense.def:
Kadar nekaj
makes an impact on a situation or person
, ima močan vpliv na določene okoliščine ali osebo.

seg.quote: ...the impact of computing on routine office work.
British authors make relatively little impact abroad.

sense.def:
The impact of one object on another
je sila, s katero en predmet zadene drugega.

seg.quote: Many modern bullets produce an explosive effect upon impact.
